Exponent Private Equity to Bid for BBC Publications, Times Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-04-10T10:09:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/exponent-private-equity-to-bid-for-bbc-publications-times-says.html
Exponent Private Equity LLP plans
to bid for a portfolio of U.K. magazines being sold by the
British Broadcasting Corp., the  Sunday Times  reported, without
saying where it got the information.  The publications may raise about 100 million pounds ($164
million), according to the report. A preferred bidder will be
chosen in the next two weeks, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London at 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Harrison at 
 mharrison5@bloomberg.net  